                 =\frac{(3-\sqrt5)(\sqrt5-1)}{32}
\]

คูณตัวเศษ:

\[
(3-\sqrt5)(\sqrt5-1)=3\sqrt5-3-5+\sqrt5
                    =4\sqrt5-8
                    =4(\sqrt5-2)
\]

ดังนั้น  

\[
\sin ^3 18^{\circ}= \frac{4(\sqrt5-2)}{32}
